{"tid":286330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廉署立案查梁振英藉周浩鼎改立會文件　周：光明正大，清者自清","createTime":"2017-06-16T13:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T07:32:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d30ffc260e2fabfc9930f7747c6302e94e49736c","tid":286330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170616/s00001/e9d56240d236d21e8e04c4a1af53e855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170616%2Fs00001%2Fe9d56240d236d21e8e04c4a1af53e855.jpg&h=8ef15450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息指，廉署已就行政長官梁振英透過民建聯議員周浩鼎修改立法會調查UGL事宜委員會文件一事展開調查。周浩鼎回應指，自己「光明正大，清者自清，毋須擔心」。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎指，有關UGL調查委員會的事，早前已經全部回應，對於廉署，他強調自己光明正大，清者自清，毋須擔心。"},{"pid":"4724f8b348ed50864147f578e08830eab55d2f5a","tid":286330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:44:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170616/s00001/1497617929083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170616%2Fs00001%2F1497617929083&d=6SNwFKqVviYZE5habXOENdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3b8d58b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170616%2Fs00001%2F1497617929083&h=73a0fa71\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170616/s00001/1497617929083</a>"},{"pid":"b3c8ef66c998aa876bcd83cfaea13f1f0029c22f","tid":286330,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f83653b7354fad6f2bb8263c2273014943648fe9","tid":286330,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"笑撚左"},{"pid":"6e9354492f1197a689a0156f10f8c4be5fbc84f9","tid":286330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT